## 13. REPLAYABILITY

### 13.1 New Game+ — P2
- [ ] Define what carries over: skills, recipes, collectible progress?
- [ ] Define what changes: harder enemies, new dialogue options, hidden content unlocked?
- [ ] New NG+ exclusive content: at minimum 1 secret car and 1 alternative quest path
- [ ] NG+ difficulty scaling: enemies scale to player level

### 13.2 Branching Path Tracking — P2
- [ ] Post-game statistics screen: choices made, companions survived, factions aligned, ending achieved
- [ ] "Road not taken" indicators: show player what they missed without spoiling specifics
- [ ] Chapter/zone select after first completion: replay individual zones with current character
- [ ] Completion percentage: per zone and total, visible in save file

### 13.3 Procedural Elements — P3
- [ ] Minor loot randomization per playthrough
- [ ] NPC placement variation for non-critical NPCs
- [ ] Optional daily/weekly challenge mode: randomly selected 10-car gauntlet with leaderboard
- [ ] Roguelike mode: permadeath, randomized car order (subset of full game), run-based unlocks

